            <h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family">
              <a href="#" class="font-choco">2. With Updo Hairstyles</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">With an updo hairstyle, you have the opportunity to showcase bold and statement jewellery yet oftentimes, less is more without the addition of long locks. Simple hoop earrings or bold stud earrings can all add some dimension to your look. Consider choosing earrings that complement the colour or style of your outfit. For earrings, check out Cassiopeia’s <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/shop-earrings/products/citrine-cut-stud-earrings">Citrine Cut Stud Earrings</a> and for necklaces, you can’t go wrong with a <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/signature-necklace/products/solaire">Solaire</a> or <a href="https://cassiopeiagems.com/collections/signature-necklace/products/ra-eye-with-white-topaz">Ra Eye with White Topaz</a> signature necklace.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-12 d-flex">
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image12 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image top6 mr-5"></div>
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image13 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image top6 mr-5"></div>
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image14 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image top6"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-center mb-top">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family">
              <a href="#" class="font-choco">Matching Necklaces with Different Hairstyles</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco mb-5">When choosing necklaces to match your hairstyle, consider the length and style of your necklace. A simple pendant necklace or choker can work great with short hair, while a long pendant necklace can complement long hair. For shoulder length hair, consider wearing a delicate chain necklace with a small pendant, or layering necklaces of different lengths. With an updo hairstyle, try wearing a bold statement necklace or a layered necklace.</p>
